      <title>加拿大投资数百万美元建设芯片网络，美国紧随其后</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/canada-invests-millions-to-build-chip-network-as-us-races-ahead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大将在五年内投资 1.2 亿加元（8820 万美元）建设国家芯片网络，与此同时，要求政府采取更多措施支持其落后的半导体行业的呼声越来越高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/canada-invests-millions-to-build-chip-network-as-us-races-ahead</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 17:35:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克的 X 因危险内容收到欧盟的最终警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/musk-s-x-to-get-final-eu-warning-over-dangerous-content</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于未能打击危险内容，埃隆·马斯克的社交媒体平台 X 将受到正式警告，这是欧盟监管机构最近几周第三次对大型科技公司采取强硬措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/musk-s-x-to-get-final-eu-warning-over-dangerous-content</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 17:19:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰央行行长将宽松预期推迟至 2026 年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/poland-s-central-bank-chief-throws-easing-expectations-into-2026</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰央行行长强化了其对通胀的立场，称政策制定者不太可能在 2026 年之前降息，因为他们预计物价将再次上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/poland-s-central-bank-chief-throws-easing-expectations-into-2026</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 16:16:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士与欧盟重启金融市场监管谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/switzerland-and-eu-resume-talks-on-financial-market-regulation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士与欧盟委员会已恢复有关金融市场监管的讨论，该讨论自 2017 年以来一直处于暂停状态，双方希望达成一项更广泛的协议来管理两国关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/switzerland-and-eu-resume-talks-on-financial-market-regulation</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 16:00:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙在关键投票前保持沉默。他的团队对此心存感激</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/macron-has-gone-quiet-ahead-of-a-key-vote-his-group-is-grateful</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃马纽埃尔·马克龙 (Emmanuel Macron) 上一次公开露面已经是五天前了。而且，在周日第二轮立法投票决定性时刻到来之前，没有迹象表明总统会露面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/macron-has-gone-quiet-ahead-of-a-key-vote-his-group-is-grateful</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 15:57:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民意调查显示勒庞将无法获得法国多数席位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/le-pen-set-to-fall-short-of-majority-in-france-polling-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据民意调查公司的预测，玛丽娜·勒庞领导的国民联盟在周日的法国立法选举中将无法获得绝对多数。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/le-pen-set-to-fall-short-of-majority-in-france-polling-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 15:00:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>葡萄牙将允许更多新居民享受税收减免</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/portugal-to-let-more-new-residents-be-eligible-for-tax-break</link>
      <description><![CDATA[葡萄牙计划允许更多新居民享受所得税减免，以吸引技术工人来到该国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/portugal-to-let-more-new-residents-be-eligible-for-tax-break</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 14:36:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
